quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,170,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀lé ohun tí Allāhu sọ̀kalẹ̀.” Wọ́n á wí pé: “Rárá, A óò máa tẹ̀lé ohun tí a bá l’ọ́wọ́ àwọn bàbá wa ni.” Ṣé pẹ̀lú bí ó ṣe jẹ́ pé àwọn bàbá wọn kò ṣe làákàyè kan kan (nípa ẹ̀sìn), tí wọn kò sì mọ̀nà?",""
  2,171,"Àpèjúwe àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ dà bí àpèjúwe ẹni tí ó ń kígbe (mọ́ ẹranko) tí kò gbọ́rọ̀ bí kò ṣe ìpè àti igbe (asán). Adití, ayaya, afọ́jú ni wọ́n; wọn kò sì níí ṣe làákàyè.",""
  2,172,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ jẹ nínú àwọn n̄ǹkan dáadáa tí A pèsè fún yín, kí ẹ sì dúpẹ́ fún Allāhu tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Òun nìkan ṣoṣo ni ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún.",""
  2,173,"Ohun tí (Allāhu) ṣe ní èèwọ̀ fún yín ni òkúǹbete<sup>1</sup>, ẹ̀jẹ̀<sup>2</sup>, ẹran ẹlẹ́dẹ̀ àti ohun tí wọ́n pe orúkọ mìíràn lé lórí yàtọ̀ sí (orúkọ) Allāhu. Ṣùgbọ́n ẹni tí ìnira (ebi) bá mú (jẹ ẹran èèwọ̀), tí kì í ṣe ẹni tó ń wá èèwọ̀ kiri àti olùtayọ-ẹnu-ààlà, kò sí ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ fún un. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.<sup>3</sup>","[1] Òkúǹbete ni ẹran tí ó kú fúnra rẹ̀. Kíyè sí i, ẹ̀tọ́ ni òkúǹbete ẹran odò ní tirẹ̀ ní ìbámu sí sūrah al-Mā’idah; 5:96. [2] Ìyẹn ẹ̀jẹ̀ tí ó tú jáde lára ẹran yálà nípasẹ̀ dídúńbú, gígún tàbí títalọ́fà ní ìbámu sí sūrah al-’Ani‘ām; 6:145. Kì í ṣe ẹ̀jẹ̀ tí ó ṣẹ́kù sára ẹran tí wọ́n ti kun tàbí ẹ̀jẹ̀ tí ó wà nínú ẹ̀dọ̀ àti àmọ́. [3] Ìnira ebi ni pé, kí ènìyàn bọ́há sí àyè kan, tí kò ti lè rí òdíwọ̀n ohun jíjẹ tàbí ohun mímu halāl tí ó kéré jùlọ láti fi gbé ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ró. Àmọ́ ní ti ìnira àìsàn, mùsùlùmí kò gbọdọ̀ lo n̄ǹkan harām láti fi tọ́jú ara rẹ̀, bí ó tilẹ̀ wù kí ó rí, kódà kó fẹ́ já sí ikú. Harām kì í ṣe sábàbí ìlera. Nítorí náà, ìnira ebi ni làlúrí. Ìnira àìsàn kì í ṣe làlúrí."
  2,174,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ń daṣọ bo ohun tí Allāhu sọ̀kalẹ̀ nínú Tírà, tí wọ́n sì ń tà á ní owó pọ́ọ́kú, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn kò jẹ kiní kan sí inú wọn bí kò ṣe Iná. Allāhu kò sì níí bá wọn sọ̀rọ̀ (ìdùnnú) ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde, kò sì níí fọ̀ wọ́n mọ́ (nínú ẹ̀ṣẹ̀). Ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro sì wà fún wọn.",""
  2,175,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn tó fi ìmọ̀nà ra ìṣìnà, (wọ́n tún fi) àforíjìn ra ìyà.<sup>1</sup> Ṣé wọn sì lè ṣèfaradà fún Iná! (Àbí kí ló kì wọ́n láyà láti ṣe iṣẹ́ Iná!)","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, wọ́n mú ìṣìnà, wọ́n fi ìmọ̀nà sílẹ̀, wọ́n mú ìyà, wọ́n sì fi àforíjìn sílẹ̀."
  2,176,"Ìyẹn rí bẹ́ẹ̀ nítorí pé dájúdájú Allāhu sọ Tírà (al-Ƙur’ān) kalẹ̀ pẹ̀lú òdodo. Dájúdájú àwọn tó sì yapa Tírà náà kúkú ti wà nínú ìyapà tó jìnnà (sí òdodo).",""
